-- Mitsui of Japan to Join 260 Million Euro Solar Power Project in Spain
-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 2010-11-05T05:40:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/mitsui-of-japan-to-join-260-million-euro-solar-power-project-in-spain.html
Mitsui & Co., a Japanese trading
company, agreed to join a 260 million euro ($369 million) solar
power project in Spain.  A European unit of Mitsui will buy 30 percent of a
subsidiary of Fomento de Construcciones y Contratas SA as part
of the deal, the Japanese company said today in a statement on
its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
